[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0607","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0607.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0369","title":"Sun Solaris OpenWindows sdtcm_convert 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中 OpenWindows 环境的 sdtcm_convert 日历转换工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向该程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 及更早版本，需要本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0369"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.910","remediation":"立即应用 Sun 安全公告 #183 提供的补丁，升级 sdtcm_convert 至修复版本。如无法打补丁，执行 `chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/sdtcm_convert` 移除 setuid 位以消除本地提权风险，或卸载 OpenWindows 组件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/183","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19128","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0369.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0369","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0369.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0369.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8rf-j665-q782/GHSA-q8rf-j665-q782.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e6c9064b-c174-46c8-964b-e6dfac38cd65.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0369.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0607.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0605","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0605.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0827","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨域导航子框架欺骗漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 及后续版本默认启用了\"跨不同域的导航子框架\"选项，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，诱使用户在浏览器中访问该页面，利用不同域之间框架导航权限控制的缺失实施框架欺骗攻击。攻击者可将目标网站嵌入恶意网页的子框架中，并通过跨域导航将子框架内容替换为任意恶意内容，导致用户混淆当前浏览页面的真实来源，进而可能被诱导输入敏感信息或进行其他危险操作。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 及后续版本，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0827"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.450","remediation":"lots of notes mixed in","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0827"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0605.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0604","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0368","title":"WU-FTPD 和 ProFTPD realpath 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd 及 ProFTPD 的 realpath 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的路径请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出并实现远程 root 权限获取。该漏洞影响 wu-ftpd 2.4.2、ProFTPD 1.2 pre1 及 SCO Open Server 5.0.5 等版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0368"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.780","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5.0 及以上版本，或升级 ProFTPD 至 1.2.0 及以上稳定版。如无法立即升级，可在 inetd/xinetd 配置中禁用 FTP 服务或限制可信任 IP 访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0368","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/REMath/implementations/blob/045b59dc77d5bd3e9a14713898ebcfdebacd11e9/tanalysis/tanalysis/verisec%20v1.0/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0368","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0368.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/westtide/open-source-case-studies/blob/57e71842cdb3e034316b0d083f8d19f680501b67/verisec/.frama-c/programs_apps_wu-ftpd_CVE-1999-0368_realpath-linkpath_prefix_ok.eva/nonterm.log","https://github.com/tomhart-msc/verisec/blob/02f3a9660885181705e7550b8609534bbbaa414c/programs/apps/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0603","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0367","title":"NetBSD netstat 本地内核内存访问漏洞","description":"NetBSD 系统的 netstat 命令存在本地内核内存泄露漏洞。由于 netstat 工具在处理网络统计信息时未能正确限制对内核内存区域的访问权限，本地攻击者可通过执行特制的 netstat 命令读取内核敏感数据，导致内核信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 NetBSD 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0367"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.657","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 NetBSD 1.4.1 的安全补丁中修复。如无法升级，可通过 chmod 700 /usr/bin/netstat 限制 netstat 命令的执行权限，仅允许 root 用户使用，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7571"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0602","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0602.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0826","title":"FreeBSD angband 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 3.3 系统中自带的游戏 angband 存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。具有本地系统访问权限的攻击者可利用该漏洞，通过向 angband 程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，实现权限提升并获得更高权限。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 3.3 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危，需要攻击者拥有本地账户。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0826"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.333","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 FreeBSD 3.3 发行版附带的 angband 游戏中，因 setuid 二进制程序存在缓冲区溢出可导致本地提权。建议升级至 FreeBSD 3.4 或更高版本，该版本已修复此问题；如无法升级，可立即执行 `chmod u-s /usr/local/bin/angband` 移除 angband 的 setuid 权限位以阻断提权路径，或直接卸载 angband 软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1151","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/840","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19653"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0602.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0745","title":"IBM AIX pdnsd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1 和 4.2 版本中 C Set++ 编译器附带的源代码浏览器程序数据库名称服务器守护进程（pdnsd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的反向 DNS 查询请求触发该溢出，导致任意代码执行或以 root 权限控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.1/4.2 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0745"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.130","remediation":"升级至 AIX 4.3 或更高版本以修复 pdnsd 缓冲区溢出漏洞；若无法升级，可停止 pdnsd 服务（/usr/bin/stopsrc -s pdnsd）并从 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释相应行后重启 inetd 以彻底禁用该服务。对于必须使用该功能的系统，建议限制对 pdnsd 端口的网络访问（如通过防火墙或 tcpwrappers）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-059.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/590","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0600.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0600.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0599","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0365","title":"Metamail mailcap 条目未过滤 shell 元字符远程命令执行漏洞","description":"metamail 邮件处理工具包中存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，在将邮件内容传递给 mailcap 条目处理时未对 shell 元字符进行正确引号转义，导致远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制邮件触发命令执行。攻击者利用该漏洞可在受害者系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令，影响广泛部署 metamail 的 Unix/Linux 系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0365"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.403","remediation":"升级 metamail 至 2.7-9 或更高版本，该版本已对 mailcap 文件中的 shell 元字符进行正确转义处理。如无法升级，可临时移除或禁用系统中所有不可信来源的 mailcap 配置项，同时限制邮件客户端自动调用 metamail 处理附件。在 sendmail 环境下，建议禁用自动执行 mailcap 条目的功能，并审查 /etc/mailcap 及用户 ~/.mailcap 中的每条规则，确保不含未引用的 shell 元字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0365.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000513.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0365.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0598","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0598.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0364","title":"Microsoft Access 97 数据库密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Microsoft Access 97 存在数据库密码明文存储漏洞，该软件在创建受密码保护的数据库时，将用户设置的数据库密码以未经加密的明文形式写入外部的 MDB 文件头部区域。本地攻击者通过文本编辑器或十六进制查看工具直接打开该 MDB 文件即可从文件二进制数据中提取完整的数据库密码，从而绕过身份验证机制完全访问受保护的数据库内容。该漏洞源于 Access 97 在设计时未对存储的密码进行加密处理，影响 Microsoft Access 97 所有版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至更高版本 Microsoft Office 或使用第三方加密工具对数据库文件进行额外保护。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0364"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.247","remediation":"Microsoft Access 97 已停止支持多年，建议立即迁移至受支持的 Microsoft 365 或 Office 2021 等现代版本。如暂时无法迁移，避免在共享网络位置存放含密码的 .mdb 文件，并使用 Windows EFS 或 BitLocker 对数据库文件所在目录进行加密，同时将数据库密码替换为 Windows 集成身份验证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91816470220259&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0364","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0364.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hvp5-q7xm-fj7p/GHSA-hvp5-q7xm-fj7p.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--80c82ddc-bc10-4574-98b0-fe5e3ff3aadf.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0598.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0597","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0597.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0825","title":"SCO Unixware 7.1 /var/mail 默认权限配置漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.1 系统中 `/var/mail` 目录的默认权限设置不当，导致本地用户可越权读取和修改其他用户的邮件文件。攻击者通过本地账号即可利用该漏洞窃取敏感通信内容或篡改邮件数据，影响系统的机密性和完整性。该漏洞需本地访问权限，攻击条件有限，CVSS 评分 3.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0825"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.210","remediation":"将 /var/mail 目录权限改为 755 (drwxr-xr-x) 并设置粘滞位 (chmod 1755 /var/mail)，各用户邮箱文件权限设为 600 (chmod 600 /var/mail/*)。升级到 UnixWare 7.1.1 或更高版本，新版本已修复默认权限过宽问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/849","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19657"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0597.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0597.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0597.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0595","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0363","title":"S.u.S.E. Linux 5.2 lpc 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 5.2 系统中的 lpc（行式打印机控制）程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 lpc 程序发送特制的输入参数触发该溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SuSE Linux 5.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于需要本地访问权限，攻击者须先拥有系统普通用户账户方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0363"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.117","remediation":"升级 SuSE Linux 至 5.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复 lpc 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，建议限制 lpc 可执行文件的 SUID 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lpc）以降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/328","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19259","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0363.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0363","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0363.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0363.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79mx-82jw-xwqh/GHSA-79mx-82jw-xwqh.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0363.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/stucco/auto-labeled-corpus/blob/26e1e3a56dbcc0f6c9c39831bd7b9dcfec6c5f2f/src/python/preprocessing/autotag/exploitdb/bugtraq_cve_correspondence.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0594","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0362","title":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 1.0.1 及 1.0.2 版本存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令，导致 FTP 服务进程异常崩溃或停止响应，从而中断正常的文件传输服务。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，受影响用户应升级至更高版本以修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0362"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.990","remediation":"升级至 WS_FTP Server 1.0.3 及以上版本可修复此漏洞；在防火墙中限制 FTP 服务端口的访问来源 IP，防止未授权远程连接发起 CWD 命令攻击。鉴于该产品版本过于老旧，建议迁移至受支持的最新版 WS_FTP Server 或替代 FTP 服务软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD02021999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/217","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/wsftp_cwd_dos.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/Ipswitch%20WS_FTP%20Server%20prior%205.0.2%20CWD%20path%20denial%20of%20service.plugin","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0593","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0593.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0823","title":"FreeBSD xmindpath 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 3.3 系统中的 xmindpath 工具存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，该工具在处理 -f 参数时未对用户输入进行有效的长度检查。本地攻击者可向 -f 参数提交特制的超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 3.3 版本，利用需要本地系统访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0823"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.957","remediation":"建议升级至 FreeBSD 3.4 或更高版本（3.3 已停止维护），该版本已修复 xmindpath 缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可执行 `chmod 0755 /usr/bin/X11/xmindpath` 移除 setuid 位，消除本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1150","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/839","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19652"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0593.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0592","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0592.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0361","title":"LaserFiche NetWare 版敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"LaserFiche for NetWare 版本以明文形式存储用户名和密码，导致邻近网络的攻击者可通过访问系统文件获取管理员凭证，造成敏感信息泄露。同时，系统允许管理员配置更改但未记录日志，使得未授权操作无法追溯审计。攻击者可利用窃取的凭证对系统进行进一步未授权访问与控制。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0361"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.863","remediation":"升级到 LaserFiche 现代版本（如 9.0 以上）以使用加密存储和审计日志功能；若无法升级，迁移至 Hyland 或其他具备加密存储与操作审计的文档管理平台。作为临时缓解措施，在网络层限制对 LaserFiche 服务的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，并在 NetWare 服务器上启用文件系统和操作审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0361.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c344